headline: Why Sally Beauty (SBH) Stock Is Up Today
summary: Shares of beauty supply retailer Sally Beauty (NYSE:SBH) jumped 3.6% in the afternoon session after investor optimism grew around the company's growth plans and a new delivery partnership.
